title: Marenum Pte Ltd
description: Marenum is a sustainable coral and tropical fish farm permaculture business based in Timor Leste.

home.title: Welcome to our coral and ornamental fish permaculture business.
home.description: Marenum is our holding company for Al-Eka Fishworld Lda which is licensed by the Ministry of Agriculture and Fish for aquaculture in Timor Leste for live ornamental fish and coral permaculture for export.  See the sections below for more details on both the corporation and our plans.
